        "TileImage": "$($repository be05317a-3d16-4b41-bede-ff99e126c157).Image",
        "Description": "Good Day 47,\rYour targets are enjoying their day and doing their work. But they are unaware that a chain of unfortunate accidents is about to unfold within the quiet efficiency of the Hokkaido facility. Routine will betray them, safety will fail them, and coincidence will turn lethal. What appears as mere misfortune will be anything but. Ensure everything looks accidental, and leave no trace behind.\r\rGood Luck.\r\rBy - SW",
